# Testing

## Framework
- React Testing Library (`@testing-library/react`, `@testing-library/user-event`)
- Jest (via react-scripts / craco)

## Conventions
- Test files: `*.test.js` or `*.test.jsx` colocated with source
- Use `render()`, `screen`, `userEvent` for component tests
- Mock Firebase: mock `firebase/initFirebase` and auth/firestore modules
- Avoid testing implementation details; focus on user behaviour

## Examples
```javascript
// Mock Firebase before importing component
jest.mock('@/firebase/initFirebase', () => ({ db: {}, firebaseAuth: {} }));
```
